# SEO — Charlotte Car Shows

## Metadata Patterns

### Required Metadata (Every Page)
- `title`: Use descriptive title (template from root layout)
- `description`: Concise, keyword-rich description
- `alternates.canonical`: Absolute URL (`https://charlottecarshows.com/...`)
- `openGraph`: title, description, url, type, images
- `twitter`: card type, title, description, images

### Metadata Example
```typescript
export const metadata: Metadata = {
  title: "Page Title | Charlotte Car Shows",
  description: "Page description here...",
  alternates: { canonical: "https://charlottecarshows.com/path/" },
  openGraph: {
    title: "Page Title",
    description: "Page description...",
    url: "https://charlottecarshows.com/path/",
    type: "website",
    images: [{ url: "https://charlottecarshows.com/images/...", alt: "..." }],
  },
  twitter: {
    card: "summary_large_image",
    title: "Page Title",
    description: "Page description...",
    images: ["https://charlottecarshows.com/images/..."],
  },
};
```

## Structured Data (JSON-LD)

