## SEO Best Practices

### URLs
- **Canonical:** Always include canonical URL (absolute)
- **Structure:** Use descriptive, keyword-rich URLs
- **Slugs:** Use kebab-case for event/venue slugs

### Images
- **Alt Text:** Always include descriptive `alt` text
- **Optimization:** Use Next.js `Image` component
- **Open Graph:** Include OG images for social sharing

### Content
- **Headings:** Use semantic heading hierarchy (h1 → h2 → h3)
- **Keywords:** Natural keyword usage in content
- **Internal Links:** Link to related pages (events, venues)

### Performance
- **Core Web Vitals:** Monitor LCP, CLS, INP
- **Lighthouse:** Target 90+ scores
- **Mobile:** Mobile-first design, test on devices

## Accessibility (Related to SEO)

### ARIA Labels
- Use `aria-label` for interactive elements without visible text
- Use `aria-current="page"` for current page in navigation
- Use `aria-hidden="true"` for decorative elements

### Semantic HTML
- Use semantic elements (`<nav>`, `<article>`, `<section>`)
- Use proper heading hierarchy
- Use descriptive link text

